<header class="blog-post-page-title">
    <h4>伪类和伪元素详解</h4>
    <time datetime="2022-04-12T15:10:05.066Z"><i class="fa fa-clock-o"></i>2022-04-12</time>
    
    
    
    
	
        <span><i class="fa fa-folder-o"></i>
    		
    	       <a href="/categories/css/" rel="categories" data-toggle="tooltip" data-placement="top" title="Linux">css</a>
    		
        </span>
	
    
</header>
